In this work, we aim to address these critical questions through an in-depth investigation into the optoelectronic properties of NaBiS2. This material is similar to AgBiS2 in that the metal atoms can be disordered across the cation sublattice to give an effective high-symmetry cubic rocksalt phase (space group: Fm3¬Ø\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
